cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "BCI Dataset Cards"
abstract: >-
  A command-line tool that generates plain-language "dataset cards" for public
  EEG/BCI datasets: leakage-aware baselines, chance level and significance,
  per-class metrics, and metadata from MOABB and EEGDash (OpenNeuro/NEMAR).
type: software
authors:
